To compile the ftserver.c file for this program:

gcc -o ftserver ftserver.c

I only tested the file with txt files. So, please only use those for grading purposes. It MAY work with other file types, but I am not sure. I did include the "rb/wb" permissions either way. 

I have cited sources when necessary with line comments in my source code. However, I did get additional, general help from these sources. They include:

	http://beej.us/guide/bgnet/output/html/singlepage/bgnet.html
	http://www.linuxhowtos.org/C_C++/socket.htm
	http://stackoverflow.com/questions/27014955/socket-connect-vs-bind